{"tid":1989171,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"渣古豬嘴(單嘴用)","createTime":"2020-04-25T17:25:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T03:35:51.000Z","uid":336922,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7db9cb956ad991d4f093dc102ce49a94f7e7aafd","tid":1989171,"uid":336922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T17:25:45.000Z","msg":"之前design 咗高達豬嘴<br />\n6500QL:<br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1981140/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1981140/page/1</a><br />\n3200 單嘴:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1984579/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1984579/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n今次就整咗渣古豬嘴比3200單嘴用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前有巴打request ga <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：今個月一毫子都冇比過Bandai<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nprint 呢個口罩bandai冇錢收ga<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eH9bu3o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeH9bu3o.jpg&h=356134ea&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nuH07P4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnuH07P4.jpg&h=52dcae44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 試戴口罩圖片:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ay3cevd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAy3cevd.jpg&h=fe3e1bd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1AoLzve.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1AoLzve.jpg&h=7f3120b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n使用方法:<br />\n打開個口罩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OjBQLJr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOjBQLJr.jpg&h=32189876&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n放一片4.5cm x 5cm 既filter<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vc3WGgN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvc3WGgN.jpg&h=be6bf683&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n放個墊圈落去<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YdmQLJt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYdmQLJt.jpg&h=fa44ae12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n扣返埋個蓋<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Eye3mgQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEye3mgQ.jpg&h=292bfdd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冚埋個口罩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6R0Fovb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6R0Fovb.jpg&h=74339e2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n製作方法:<br />\n需要10粒 m3 10mm 螺絲<br />\nm3 10mm 螺絲x4<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5txXqEE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5txXqEE.jpg&h=0c4e271f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nm3 10mm 螺絲x2<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PTSHBMj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPTSHBMj.jpg&h=6851dd4a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nm3 10mm 螺絲x2<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WCaesS0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWCaesS0.jpg&h=562722a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nm3 10mm 螺絲x2<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qPGtxjG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqPGtxjG.jpg&h=2edfab36&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1Xt_NLNHEY8fGITyoN4DrC-zX7j-Kx0Rp?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Ffolders%2F1Xt_NLNHEY8fGITyoN4DrC-zX7j-Kx0Rp%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=lW7zubw4D25L16l94wxnCh6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=56b97076\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1Xt_NLNHEY8fGITyoN4DrC-zX7j-Kx0Rp?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n都係提醒返大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">發夢就唔好用啦</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n